ass=title> Born of Flame,Tales of a Wizard</span><hr size=1> <br>
 The gods are at war !<br>
This shout was echoed across the dark forest of Nektulous.<br>
The gods are at war !<br>
Again it reverberated off the mountain passes to Lavastorm, the very trees of the dark woods seeming to take up the cry. <br>
<br>
Inside the dark city of Neriak deep in it's heart at the temple of Innoruuk the high priest sat in meditation, her priests gathered fearfully around her.Awaiting a sign from her dark god she continued her prayers.Then she paled her sign had come..... Innoruuk was defeated and forced to retreat to his dark home.... <br>
<br>
In another dark chamber a group of enshrouded figures chanted quietly. The smell of rot clinging to their heavy robes skeletons sat restlessly around them awaiting their commands...none were to come.With a piercing scream the lich that had been leading the chanting pitched forward his last words our lord has fallen.....<br>
<br>
A group of warriors sat around a table the smell of ale filling the large chamber as they threw dice. Laughter and shouts filled the hall when a disheveled figure rushed into the room, covered in blood and panting breathlessly. The others in the room were silent as they regarded him awaiting what had brought him forth in such a state. His news was dark indeed... The mighty Rallos Zek was defeated....<br>
<br>
A mighty sorcerer sat in a brightly lit room a large gathering of robed figures before him. These were the spurned of Innoruuk the casters who forsook the dark art of necromancy. These were the mages, enchanters and wizards. Silently they sat watching the sorcerer as he scanned Norrath with his mystic eye searching for a sign of Solusek Ro.Suddenly he paled...<br>
&quot;What is wrong lord&quot; ? a young wizard asked.<br>
&quot;I will show you&quot; was his only response before he began to mutter.<br>
<br>
The gathering suddenly found themselves upon the burning sands of South Ro looking out from the wizards spire at....a world in choas.Fires rained from the heavens the ground erupted in fury, bodies of the foul light races flew in all directions.In the center of this storm stood a beleaguered form hard pressed on all sides by the light races and before any could react they saw him fall the flames in his eyes dying as he dropped.This was the fall of Solosek Ro...<br>
<br>
The gathering of lights rejoiced in their victory and were quick to begin looting the once mighty lord. However he was not yet done with them....<br>
<br>
A portal snapped open the fires of hell poured forth upon the gathered light army. Storms of lightning flashed from the sky piercing elves and humans in quick devastating blows.The fires consumed the bodies of Dwarves and Halflings.Even the dark races at the spires were not spared all was consumed in a wave of destruction,and from this flame emerged a figure...<br>
<br>
Completely untouched by the fires and lightning walking through the rain of destruction the form came to stand before the last of the darks at the spire, the sorcerer among them.<br>
The form was a dark elf,naked as a newborn he stood before the assembled drow and looked at each in turn then in a thunderous voice that echoed across the desert declared...<br>
<br>
&quot; I am Xavar Helfyre. Born of the flames of war I have been sent to destroy those who would slay our dark race and your masters.May the light fall and darkness rule all... <br>
 <br>
 ----------------------------------------------------------- The previous passage was the first chapter of Born of Flames,Tales of a wizard. I myself do not write the story into the book. The book writes the events itself. The Sorcerer who met me at the Spire, (who later became my mentor in the arts of Wizardry) created this book immediately upon our arrival back in Neriak. He proclaimed that I was the Lord of Chaos and that my arrival meant a return to a world of darkness. He created the book to magically copy my life as it unfolded. It is difficult to obtain a full transcript as the book is always writing. What I post here for you all is what I am able to copy before the page changes again.<br>
<br>
Xavar Helfyre,The Prince of Hell<br>
.... there is no knowledge that is not power,and power is where I excel...<br>
